<chapter id="gs-cisco-asa-pix">
  <title>Getting Started: Configuring Cisco ASA and PIX Firewalls</title>
  <para>
  Firewall Builder is a configuration management application  
  used to configure and manage firewall rules for multiple types of firewalls. 
  This guide  goes through the steps necessary  to create a Cisco ASA firewall object 
  in Firewall Builder, and then install rules created in 
  Firewall Builder onto the firewall.
